# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:20
translate chinese jez13_b18520d8:

    # "As I lie down to go to sleep, my cell phone starts buzzing in my pocket. I pull it out and see a text from Jez."
    "当我躺下准备睡觉时，口袋里的手机开始震动。我掏出来，看到杰兹发来的短信。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:27
translate chinese jez13_1c825c30:

    # "She needs me? What is this about?"
    "她找我？这是怎么回事？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:30
translate chinese jez13_fcdca668:

    # "I send her a text back, but I'm already standing up and getting ready to leave."
    "我回了她一条短信，但其实已经站起身准备出门了。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:37
translate chinese jez13_e4c1f4a7:

    # "By the time I'm in my car and driving to her house, she still hasn't texted me again, and I'm getting very worried."
    "等我坐进车里开往她家时，她还没再发消息给我，我开始非常担心。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:40
translate chinese jez13_507bb3e8:

    # "At her house, I rush up the sidewalk and knock loudly on the door."
    "到了她家，我快步走上人行道，用力敲响了门。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:41
translate chinese jez13_e644f7dc:

    # "I wait a few moments for a response, but there's only silence."
    "我等了一会儿，却只听到一片寂静。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:42
translate chinese jez13_f1357f96:

    # "Feeling very weird about it, I turn the handle on her door, finding it unlocked, and open it just slightly."
    "感觉很不对劲，我转动门把手，发现门没锁，便轻轻推开了一条缝。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:45
translate chinese jez13_bf40788d:

    # "I peek inside. All the lights are off."
    "我往里张望。屋里所有的灯都关着。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:46
translate chinese jez13_1bb756e1:

    # pc "Jez?"
    pc "杰兹？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:47
translate chinese jez13_877b07f6:

    # "I call out, but I still don't hear any answer."
    "我喊了一声，但依然没有得到回应。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:48
translate chinese jez13_d12b4849:

    # "I can hear something inside though. Running water."
    "不过我听见屋里有动静。是流水声。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:49
translate chinese jez13_7dad49af:

    # pc "Jez? Are you okay?"
    pc "杰兹？你没事吧？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:52
translate chinese jez13_fcc96292:

    # "Nervous, I walk inside."
    "我紧张地走了进去。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:53
translate chinese jez13_0ba6f0af:

    # "Down the hall, I see a light coming from a mostly closed door. That's where the running water sound is coming from too."
    "走廊尽头，一扇半开的门缝里透出微光。流水声也是从那里传来的。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:54
translate chinese jez13_13bdec20:

    # pc "Jez, it's [pcname]. I'm coming in."
    pc "杰兹，是我[pcname]。我要进来了。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:55
translate chinese jez13_29614313:

    # pc "Is everything okay?"
    pc "一切都还好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:56
translate chinese jez13_61906623:

    # "Still no reply."
    "依然没有回应。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:57
translate chinese jez13_5689c553:

    # "When I get to the bathroom, I open the door slightly and peek in."
    "走到浴室门口，我轻轻推开门缝往里张望。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:60
translate chinese jez13_c5d4c21c:

    # "I find Jez, sitting on the floor of the shower, holding her head and sobbing."
    "只见杰兹坐在淋浴间的地板上，双手抱头，啜泣不止。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:61
translate chinese jez13_9824f7a8:

    # pc "Jez, what's wrong?"
    pc "杰兹，怎么了？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:62
translate chinese jez13_f8c74a4a:

    # "I rush in towards her."
    "我冲过去抱住她。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:66
translate chinese jez13_7779e5b0:

    # "I kneel down next to her, water spraying all over me, soaking my clothing."
    "我跪在她身旁，水花四溅，淋湿了我的衣服。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:67
translate chinese jez13_96cc75fe:

    # pc "Jez, what happened? Are you okay?"
    pc "杰兹，发生了什么？你还好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:69
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_1.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_1.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:70
translate chinese jez13_c5d023e4:

    # det "Please, just hold me. No talking."
    det "求你了，抱紧我。别说话。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:71
translate chinese jez13_880b4aa8:

    # pc "Okay..."
    pc "好……"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:74
translate chinese jez13_b0b9d042:

    # "She leans into me, her body folding up on itself, crumpling like a paper ball."
    "她把身体蜷缩在我怀里，像个纸团一样瘫软下来。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:75
translate chinese jez13_57b2ed32:

    # "She cries so hard. I've never seen anybody cry like this."
    "她哭得那么伤心。我从未见过有人这样哭。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:76
translate chinese jez13_b3e695dd:

    # "Like a dam bursting, like she had been holding it in for so long."
    "就像大坝决堤，仿佛她已经压抑了太久。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:77
translate chinese jez13_fc8296d1:

    # "Her body trembles and I just try to hug her and hold her and rub her back and assure her that everything is going to be okay."
    "她的身体在颤抖，我只能紧紧拥抱她，抚摸她的背，告诉她一切都会好起来的。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:78
translate chinese jez13_a971ab79:

    # "Even though I don't know what is wrong and I have no idea if she'll ever be okay again."
    "尽管我不知道出了什么事，也不知道她是否还能恢复如常。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:79
translate chinese jez13_8cb501d6:

    # "I don't know how long we sit there like that, before she finally starts breathing normally and she looks up at me."
    "我们就这样坐了多久，我也不清楚，直到她终于恢复了正常的呼吸，抬头看着我。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:82
translate chinese jez13_2788f6e6:

    # det "I'm sorry. I got you all wet."
    det "“对不起，我弄湿你了。”"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:83
translate chinese jez13_d4c3a46e:

    # pc "That doesn't matter. I just want to know that you're okay."
    pc "“没关系。我只想确认你没事。”"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:84
translate chinese jez13_a5f1c96b:

    # det "I had a really bad day at work."
    det "“今天工作上出了大问题。”"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:85
translate chinese jez13_13896d8c:

    # det "I feel like I can stand up now at least."
    det "“至少现在我觉得能站起来了。”"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:86
translate chinese jez13_71091f24:

    # det "Get out of those wet clothes and I'll put them in the dryer."
    det "“把湿衣服脱下来，我放进烘干机里。”"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:89
translate chinese jez13_19801827:

    # "I strip out of my clothes and a couple of minutes later, we're lying naked in her bed, my arms wrapped around her."
    "我脱下衣服，几分钟后，我们赤身裸体地躺在她床上，我双臂环抱着她。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:90
translate chinese jez13_8892cc69:

    # pc "Do you want to talk about whatever happened?"
    pc "你想聊聊刚才发生的事吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:92
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_1:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_2.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_2.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:93
translate chinese jez13_66e2454b:

    # det "I, uh... I see bad stuff at work all the time."
    det "我，呃……我在工作中经常看到糟糕的事情。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:95
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_2:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_3.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_3.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:96
translate chinese jez13_d62b2984:

    # det "Bad people doing bad things, you know?"
    det "坏人做坏事，你知道的？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:98
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_3:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_4.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_4.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:99
translate chinese jez13_cec0c1d1:

    # det "Most of the time it doesn't get to me."
    det "大多数时候我不会受影响。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:101
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_4:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_5.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_5.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:102
translate chinese jez13_79ca3fcc:

    # det "But sometimes I see these horrible things that happen to good people."
    det "但有时我看到这些可怕的事情发生在好人身上。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:104
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_5:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_6.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_6.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:105
translate chinese jez13_9629a00a:

    # det "To children..."
    det "发生在孩子身上……"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:107
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_6:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_7.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_7.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:108
translate chinese jez13_edb2340e:

    # det "And I feel like this world isn't worth living in."
    det "我就觉得这个世界不值得活了。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:112
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_7:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_8.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_8.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:113
translate chinese jez13_5562c66c:

    # det "I saw some horrible shit at work today."
    det "今天我在工作中看到了一些可怕的事情。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:115
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_8:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_9.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_9.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:116
translate chinese jez13_518e8f66:

    # det "I thought I could hold it together."
    det "我以为自己还能撑住。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:118
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_9:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_10.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_10.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:119
translate chinese jez13_1916d72b:

    # det "I came home and hugged Javi for a long time before I put him to bed."
    det "回家后，我在哄哈维睡觉前抱了他好久。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:121
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_10:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_11.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_11.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:122
translate chinese jez13_502389b1:

    # det "Then when I got in the shower, something in my head snapped."
    det "然后当我走进淋浴间时，脑子里某根弦突然断了。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:124
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_11:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_12.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_12.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:125
translate chinese jez13_da2d853a:

    # det "I couldn't breathe, I couldn't stand. I just wanted to scream and cry."
    det "我喘不过气，站不稳。只想尖叫和哭泣。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:129
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_12:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_13.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_13.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:130
translate chinese jez13_0bd213c2:

    # det "Thank you for coming. For being there for me."
    det "谢谢你过来。谢谢你一直陪着我。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:131
translate chinese jez13_a6a3e353:

    # pc "Of course. Do you need to talk to somebody professionally though? Or go to the hospital maybe?"
    pc "当然。不过你是不是该找专业人士聊聊？或者去医院看看？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:133
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_13:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_14.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_14.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:134
translate chinese jez13_f9a943bd:

    # det "I think I'm okay right now. We have a trauma counselor at work. I'm seeing her tomorrow to talk about everything."
    det "我觉得我现在还好。公司有位创伤咨询师，明天我会去找她，把一切都说出来。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:135
translate chinese jez13_af09086d:

    # pc "That's good."
    pc "那很好。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:137
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_14:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_15.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_15.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:138
translate chinese jez13_abf471b9:

    # det "Can you stay? I don't want to be alone tonight."
    det "你能留下来吗？今晚我不想一个人待着。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:139
translate chinese jez13_1fd61d7b:

    # pc "Yeah, I can stay."
    pc "嗯，我可以留下来。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:142
translate chinese jez13_539e05a9:

    # "I hold her like that for a long time and we don't really talk much more."
    "我这样抱着她很久，我们没再多说什么。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:143
translate chinese jez13_6164b0d0:

    # "She quickly falls asleep, hard."
    "她很快就睡着了，睡得很沉。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:144
translate chinese jez13_58fa8ee0:

    # "All that crying must have exhausted her completely."
    "刚才那阵哭泣一定让她彻底精疲力尽了。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:147
translate chinese jez13_11b7b1de:

    # "It takes a while longer, but eventually I fall asleep too."
    "过了好一会儿，我终于也睡着了。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:151
translate chinese jez13_1f5130c9:

    # "In the morning, I wake up with a hand on my shoulder."
    "早上醒来时，感觉有只手搭在我的肩上。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:153
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_15:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_16.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_16.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:154
translate chinese jez13_ccc69a9e:

    # det "Wake up, papi."
    det "醒醒，papi。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:155
translate chinese jez13_fe0bdf4c:

    # pc "Good morning."
    pc "早上好。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:156
translate chinese jez13_99f2649e:

    # det "I put your clothes on the bed there. They should be all dry."
    det "我把你的衣服放在那边的床上。应该都干了。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:157
translate chinese jez13_d8cdc3e9:

    # pc "Oh thanks."
    pc "哦，谢谢。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:160
translate chinese jez13_c6cc6092:

    # det "My mamá is here, in the kitchen with Javi. Are you okay with meeting them?"
    det "我妈妈来了，正在厨房里和哈维一起。你愿意见见他们吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:161
translate chinese jez13_0b87cffe:

    # pc "Are {i}you{/i} okay with it?"
    pc "{i}你{/i}愿意吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:162
translate chinese jez13_e0caa061:

    # det "Yeah, I think I am. I already told Mamá you were here."
    det "嗯，我想可以。我已经跟妈妈说你在这里了。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:163
translate chinese jez13_5069ef9a:

    # pc "Then yeah, let's do this."
    pc "那好吧，我们就去吧。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:164
translate chinese jez13_4b90fc82:

    # det "Good. Mamá is making revoltillo. I'm sure you'll love it."
    det "好。妈妈在做“revoltillo”。我敢肯定你会喜欢的。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:165
translate chinese jez13_ff89b162:

    # pc "I don't know what that means, but it sounds delicious when you say it."
    pc "我不知道那是什么意思，但听你这么说，听起来很美味。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:168
translate chinese jez13_2f2eb37e:

    # det "Mamá is probably going to drill you some. It's just what she does, sorry."
    det "妈妈大概会考考你。她就是这样，抱歉。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:169
translate chinese jez13_8994460a:

    # pc "I think I'll be okay."
    pc "我觉得我没问题。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:170
translate chinese jez13_cac39c9b:

    # det "You'll do great. Then later, maybe I'll let you drill me a bit too."
    det "你会表现得很棒的。等会儿，也许我也会让你考考我。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:171
translate chinese jez13_c805d829:

    # pc "I like that idea."
    pc "我喜欢这个主意。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:174
translate chinese jez13_bc882bad:

    # det "Javi, Mamá, I want you to meet my boyfriend, [pcname]."
    det "哈维，妈妈，我想让你见见我的男朋友，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:175
translate chinese jez13_d6a96c73:

    # mama "Buenos días, [pcname]."
    mama "早上好，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:176
translate chinese jez13_cac0ee49:

    # "She turns to Javi, who has his head down, focused on eating."
    "她转向哈维，他正低着头专心吃饭。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:177
translate chinese jez13_9a0ee5c1:

    # mama "Tell him good morning, mijo."
    mama "跟他说声早上好，孩子。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:178
translate chinese jez13_6b030f59:

    # jav "Good morning."
    jav "早上好。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:179
translate chinese jez13_fe0bdf4c_1:

    # pc "Good morning."
    pc "早上好。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:180
translate chinese jez13_da4440c4:

    # det "Have a seat and I'll make you a plate."
    det "请坐，我给你盛一盘。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:183
translate chinese jez13_7d92ea12:

    # "I sit down at the table in the empty chair next to Javi, while Jez walks over to the kitchen."
    "我坐在餐桌旁哈维旁边的空椅子上，而杰兹走向厨房。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:184
translate chinese jez13_165be96c:

    # jav "Are you living here now?"
    jav "“你现在住在这里吗？”"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:185
translate chinese jez13_d3f55d8e:

    # det "No, mijo, he's not living here. But you might see him sometimes. Is that okay?"
    det "“不，孩子，他不住在这里。但你可能会偶尔见到他。这样可以吗？”"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:186
translate chinese jez13_b4d9cdcc:

    # jav "I guess."
    jav "“大概吧。”"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:187
translate chinese jez13_bd0e121b:

    # jav "Do you like Minecraft?"
    jav "“你喜欢《我的世界》吗？”"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:188
translate chinese jez13_e961c690:

    # pc "I've never played it."
    pc "“我从来没玩过。”"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:189
translate chinese jez13_376c3872:

    # jav "Oh, I could show you how to play if you want."
    jav "“哦，如果你想的话，我可以教你怎么玩。”"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:190
translate chinese jez13_5b20795d:

    # pc "Sure, that sounds fun."
    pc "“当然，听起来很有趣。”"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:191
translate chinese jez13_9e8c872b:

    # jav "Okay, let's go!"
    jav "“好，我们开始吧！”"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:192
translate chinese jez13_2ba8fd61:

    # det "Not right now, mijo. We're having breakfast and then you have to go to school."
    det "“现在不行，孩子。我们正在吃早餐，之后你还要去上学。”"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:193
translate chinese jez13_bd2f8227:

    # jav "Okay, I'll show you later then."
    jav "好的，那我等会儿再教你。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:196
translate chinese jez13_ce637d21:

    # "Jez and her mamá come to the table and Jez puts a plate of food in front of me."
    "杰兹和她妈妈走到餐桌旁，杰兹在我面前放了一盘食物。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:197
translate chinese jez13_e02b004c:

    # "Before I get a chance to even look at it though, Mamá sits across from me and looks me in the eyes, like she's weighing me up."
    "不过在我还没来得及看那盘食物之前，妈妈就坐在我对面，直勾勾地盯着我的眼睛，好像在打量我似的。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:198
translate chinese jez13_0711ba82:

    # mama "So, [pcname], how old are you?"
    mama "那么，[pcname]，你多大了？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:200
translate chinese jez13_c2113814:

    # pc "Twenty-two."
    pc "二十二岁。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:202
translate chinese jez13_a6d70d6c:

    # mama "So young. You're younger than Jesabela."
    mama "这么年轻。你比杰萨贝拉还小。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:205
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_16:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_17.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_17.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:206
translate chinese jez13_8cc38855:

    # det "Ay Mamá!"
    det "哎，妈妈！"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:208
translate chinese jez13_1da93989:

    # mama "Do you have a job?"
    mama "你有工作吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:210
translate chinese jez13_748e9a7f:

    # pc "Yes, as an assistant at a law office."
    pc "有，在一家律师事务所当助理。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:212
translate chinese jez13_23a217be:

    # mama "Do you have any children?"
    mama "你有孩子吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:214
translate chinese jez13_4219f3ee:

    # pc "No."
    pc "没有。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:216
translate chinese jez13_5dc9c07e:

    # mama "Do you do drugs?"
    mama "你吸毒吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:218
translate chinese jez13_4219f3ee_1:

    # pc "No."
    pc "不。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:220
translate chinese jez13_af0ca811:

    # mama "Do you live with your parents?"
    mama "你和父母住在一起吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:222
translate chinese jez13_9af16977:

    # pc "I live with my [mother] at the moment."
    pc "我现在和我的[mother]住在一起。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:224
translate chinese jez13_6b1ebe90:

    # mama "How many other girlfriends do you have?"
    mama "你还有多少个女朋友？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:227
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_17:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_17b.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_17b.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:228
translate chinese jez13_5296d8b8:

    # det "Ay Mamá, be nice!"
    det "哎，妈妈，别这样！"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:229
translate chinese jez13_5faa2282:

    # mama "Que?"
    mama "什么？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:230
translate chinese jez13_fd390a20:

    # mama "Quiero saber acerca de este chico con el que estás saliendo."
    mama "我想了解你正在约会的这个男孩。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:232
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_18:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_18.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_18.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:233
translate chinese jez13_1e7215a5:

    # det "Ya te hablé de él. Es un buen chico y me gusta. ¿No confías en mi juicio?"
    det "我已经跟你提过他了。他是个好孩子，我也喜欢他。你不相信我的判断吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:234
translate chinese jez13_28dfbcd6:

    # mama "No lo hiciste tan bien la primera vez."
    mama "你第一次选得可没这么好。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:235
translate chinese jez13_1847687a:

    # det "Mamá!"
    det "妈妈！"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:237
translate chinese jez13_a9618f8c:

    # mama "Do you have any brothers or sisters?"
    mama "你有兄弟姐妹吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:239
translate chinese jez13_b0e9cb79:

    # pc "Just Suzy, my [sister]."
    pc "只有苏西，我的[sister]。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:241
translate chinese jez13_0acf000d:

    # mama "What are you going to school for?"
    mama "你上学是学什么的？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:243
translate chinese jez13_04c35adf:

    # pc "Quantum physics. To be a scientist."
    pc "量子物理。想当科学家。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:245
translate chinese jez13_36e29056:

    # det "That's enough, Mamá, the food is getting cold while you're grilling him."
    det "够了，妈妈，你这样盘问他，饭都要凉了。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:246
translate chinese jez13_9fda17f8:

    # mama "You seem like a good boy, I suppose."
    mama "我觉得你好像是个好孩子。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:247
translate chinese jez13_45d2cbc0:

    # det "He is. He helped me out a lot last night."
    det "他确实是。昨晚他帮了我大忙。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:248
translate chinese jez13_f3a75866:

    # mama "I'm sure he did."
    mama "我肯定他帮了。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:250
translate chinese jez13_d41d8cd9_19:

    # voice 'voices/jez_13_20.mp3'
    voice 'voices/jez_13_20.mp3'

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:251
translate chinese jez13_b535f103:

    # det "Mamá! Cuida lo que dices delante de Javi."
    det "妈妈！哈维在场时注意说话。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:252
translate chinese jez13_c913be1a:

    # mama "No dije nada en absoluto!"
    mama "我根本什么都没说！"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:255
translate chinese jez13_c5ef0cc4:

    # mama "If Jesabela likes you enough to introduce you to me, you must be something special."
    mama "既然杰萨贝拉喜欢你到愿意把你介绍给我，你一定很特别。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:256
translate chinese jez13_48aa3884:

    # mama "You just be good to her."
    mama "你只要对她好就行。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:257
translate chinese jez13_f31ca3be:

    # pc "Yes ma'am, I will."
    pc "是的，女士，我会的。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:258
translate chinese jez13_8faa40cf:

    # mama "No ma'am. You call me Mamá, or Ivelisse."
    mama "不，女士。你叫我妈妈，或者伊维莉丝。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:259
translate chinese jez13_49e790d0:

    # jav "Or Abuelita."
    jav "或者阿布埃利塔。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:262
translate chinese jez13_f9207776:

    # mama "No, mi guapo, you're the only one that gets to call me abuelita."
    mama "不，我的帅哥，只有你才能叫我阿布埃利塔。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:263
translate chinese jez13_8d2fe2d9:

    # jav "Oh okay. Sorry, [pcname], you can't call her that."
    jav "哦，好的。对不起，[pcname]，你不能这么叫她。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:266
translate chinese jez13_196bac72:

    # "We chit-chat a little more while we eat."
    "我们边吃边闲聊了一会儿。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:267
translate chinese jez13_dedcdede:

    # "Ivelisse is a little intimidating, but after a while, she smiles a lot and she seems pretty funny."
    "伊维莉丝起初有点让人望而生畏，但过了一会儿，她笑得很开心，看起来挺风趣的。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:268
translate chinese jez13_0ba3754f:

    # "And I can feel so much love between the three of them."
    "而且我能感受到他们三人之间浓浓的爱意。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:271
translate chinese jez13_81657b80:

    # "Javi talks a lot about school and the base that he and his friends are building in Minecraft."
    "哈维聊了很多关于学校的事，还有他和朋友们在《我的世界》里建造的基地。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:272
translate chinese jez13_c3923da8:

    # "Meanwhile, Jez looks at me with a shy smile while her foot rubs against my leg under the table."
    "与此同时，杰萨贝拉带着羞涩的微笑看着我，桌子底下她的脚正轻轻蹭着我的腿。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:275
translate chinese jez13_c332134e:

    # "When we finish eating, I tell Javi and Ivelisse goodbye."
    "吃完饭后，我跟哈维和伊维莉丝道别。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:276
translate chinese jez13_eac1a598:

    # mama "It was very nice to meet you, [pcname]."
    mama "很高兴认识你，[pcname]。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:277
translate chinese jez13_a7f3d1fc:

    # pc "Nice to meet you too. Thank you for the amazing breakfast."
    pc "我也一样。谢谢你准备的这顿美妙的早餐。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:278
translate chinese jez13_6ad487d2:

    # jav "Bye, [pcname]!"
    jav "再见，[pcname]！"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:279
translate chinese jez13_5f653b3b:

    # pc "Bye, Javi. I'll be back for you to teach me about Minecraft sometime, okay?"
    pc "再见，哈维。我改天会再来找你教我玩《我的世界》，好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:280
translate chinese jez13_930b665f:

    # jav "Okay!"
    jav "好的！"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:283
translate chinese jez13_12a645a9:

    # pc "Do you think I did okay?"
    pc "你觉得我表现得怎么样？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:284
translate chinese jez13_e66be0b3:

    # det "You did wonderful."
    det "你表现得棒极了。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:287
translate chinese jez13_2a95c68b:

    # det "Seriously, [pcname]. Thank you for everything."
    det "真的，[pcname]。谢谢你的一切。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:288
translate chinese jez13_a05c3ddb:

    # pc "You're welcome. Hope your day is better today."
    pc "不客气。希望你今天过得更好。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:289
translate chinese jez13_37df78b6:

    # det "It will be. I already feel so much better."
    det "会的。我现在已经感觉好多了。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:290
translate chinese jez13_95715fb7:

    # det "You have a good day too. Let's spend some more time together soon, okay?"
    det "你也过个好日子。我们很快再一起玩，好吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:291
translate chinese jez13_2951ed74:

    # pc "Definitely."
    pc "当然。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:294
translate chinese jez13_01f6f4f8:

    # "I leave her house and go home to change clothes and get my things, then head straight to school, barely getting there in time for my first class."
    "我离开她家，回家换了衣服拿了东西，然后直奔学校，刚好赶上第一节课。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:295
translate chinese jez13_24a3ded4:

    # "The whole time, I'm thinking about my relationship with Jez."
    "一路上，我都在想我和杰兹的关系。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:296
translate chinese jez13_b509de35:

    # "She called me her boyfriend."
    "她叫我“男朋友”。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:297
translate chinese jez13_b197b664:

    # "It seems like it's starting to get pretty serious. Meeting her kid and her mom like that."
    "看来这关系开始变得挺认真的了。像那样见到她的孩子和她妈妈。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:298
translate chinese jez13_4e167340:

    # "I have to think about if that's something I really want or not. She's amazing, but am I really ready to commit to something like that?"
    "我得好好想想，这到底是不是我真正想要的。她很棒，但我真的准备好投入这样一段关系了吗？"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:299
translate chinese jez13_3bf96260:

    # "I'll need to decide soon. I don't want to hurt her."
    "我得尽快做决定。我不想伤害她。"

# game/Scenes/Jez/jez13.rpy:300
translate chinese jez13_3c440e53:

    # "And I don't want her Mamá to hurt me."
    "也不想让她妈妈伤害我。"

